data.description: Look no further than this sundrenched and spacious 5 bedroom colonial, nestled in the serene Potomac Woods community. Walk up to the inviting front porch with space to sit and watch the sunset. Main entryway greets you with slate flooring (2020), powder room, generous size living room, dining room, and family room with fireplace (serviced and sealed in 2020). Sliding doors to the deck and level fenced backyard. Table space kitchen with white cabinets and granite countertops and stainless steel appliances. 2 car attached garage. Upper level has 5 generously sized bedrooms with plenty of closet space. Renovated hall bath. Master bedroom features a walk-in closet and fully updated bath. Lower level includes a partially finished area perfect for bonus room, exercise room or office space. Unfinished area offers plenty of storage space, laundry and utilities. Recessed lighting. Windows 2020. Exterior paint 2021. All floors refinished in 2019. HVAC 2016. Water heater 2014. Front roof replaced 2021. Enjoy convenient public transportation options and easy access to major routes. Meticulously maintained and renovated - truly a place to call home.
